<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Jefferson State awards credit for Advanced Placement Courses taken in high school with scores of 3 or higher earned on the national examinations of the College Entrance Examination Board Advanced Placement Program.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.jeffstateonline.com/Catalog/index.aspx" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
</p>

